itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:36:56.000Z","msg":"我個fd 發夢見工比人帶咗上去 旺角恒利中心三樓一出lift門對住個間 / 中匯商業大廈18-20樓 <br />\n<br />\n我個fd 發夢only，如有類同，實屬巧合。 連仔唔好del 我AC.<br />\n<br />\n以下 LIink 內有我個fd 嘅發夢內容，有該公司大量傳銷人員資料（有男有女)  + 有該公司大量行騙手法詳情(圖片+文）。<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7155464/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7155464%2Fpage%2F1&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=e2f31397\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7155464/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"f70c3380a1c20cfd4a39e59518667ea0a8d5a357","tid":1000182,"uid":193220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T06:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e435c05537a65ff6b5bbd34a9e07cda6a592b606","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fea28e54e6f0e567de4c8f53ea783e093f1aafd4","tid":1000182,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T19:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58c42242e161af1e5929229f1a484ab8a0412b1","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d71ad9a986df0bc2496604a5ed86f5ba61f583ad","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8019e70cd312237458a680ccd9f17a096180aa4b","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84e3c1816b1809b11483478f32ef081783fdf7e0","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T15:21:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf8a4d84a21b61f84c154f522a3f74999d78f5b3","tid":1000182,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有HKQF（香港資歷架構）的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=ec22621c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=1f20a49f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMOdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=167268a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"42c3432bdb6cd70be56f6e9381c305fcdfa0d37b","tid":1000182,"uid":250688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T13:46:54.000Z","msg":